\end_inset

 computed from the full HOD galaxy mock (labeled as 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

data
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

) with 
\begin_inset Formula $M_{cut}=12.9$
\end_inset

